<template>
    {{ blog.title }}
</template>

<script>
export default {
    data() {
        return {
            id: this.$route.params.id
        }
    },
    computed: {
        blog() {
            console.log(this.id)
            return this.$store.getters.getBlogById(this.id)
        }
    }
}
</script>
